House Resolution 630
By: Representatives LaHood of the 175th, Corbett of the 174th, and Burchett of the 176th
A RESOLUTION
1 Recognizing and commending Franklin Bailey; and for other purposes.
2 WHEREAS, Franklin Bailey is a 34-year member of both the Home Builders Association
3 of South Georgia (HBASG) and the Home Builders Association of Georgia (HBAG), where
4 he currently serves as the 2024-2025 president; and
5 WHEREAS, under his leadership as president, the HBAG has continued to create, promote,
6 and protect a thriving environment for affordable housing while encouraging integrity and
7 community engagement among its members; and
8 WHEREAS, with 43 years of experience in the construction industry, he further serves as the
9 owner and founder of Franklin Bailey Construction LLC; and
10 WHEREAS, Franklin Bailey has earned many accolades within the home building
11 community, including the 2018 HBASG Lifetime Hall of Famer Award and the 2010
12 HBASG Presidential Choice Award, and he is the only builder in the organization's history
13 to be honored four times as the HBASG Builder Member of the Year; and
